 Renzetti]]\n| [[Graeme Revell]]\n| [[Cory Lerios]]<hr>[[John D'Andrea]]\n| Graeme Revell\n| [[Pino Donaggio]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Joseph LoDuca]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[Bear McCreary]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! Cinematography\n| [[Bill Butler (cinematographer)|Bill Butler]]\n| [[Stefan Czapsky]]\n| [[John R. Leonetti]]\n| [[Peter Pau]]\n| Vernon Layton\n| colspan=\"2\" | Michael Marshall\n| [[Brendan Uegama]]\n|-\n! Editor(s)\n| Edward Warschilka<hr>Roy E. Peterson\n| Edward Warschilka\n| Scott Wallace<hr>Edward A. Warschilka Jr.\n| David Wu<hr>Randy Bricker\n| [[Chris Dickens]]\n| [[James Coblentz]]\n| Randy Bricker\n| Tom Elkins\n|- \n! rowspan=\"2\" | Production company\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[United Artists]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/MovieDetails/58582|title=Child's Play  (1988)|work=[[AFI Catalog of Feature Films]]|access-date=January 27, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Living Doll Productions<ref>{{cite web|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/moviedetails/58442?sid=a4146a24-678a-451b-b65d-41432d95ff02&sr=3.9871213&cp=1&pos=0|title=Child's Play 2  (1990)|work=[[AFI Catalog of Feature Films]]|access-date=January 27, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Universal Pictures]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/moviedetails/58797?sid=ebb97ace-4207-4592-be85-9f4bd1801423&sr=4.055705&cp=1&pos=0|title=Child's Play 3  (1991)|work=[[AFI Catalog of Feature Films]]|access-date=January 27, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[David Kirschner|David Kirschner Productions]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/MovieDetails/60656|title=Bride of Chucky  (1998)|work=[[AFI Catalog of Feature Films]]|access-date=January 27, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | La Sienega Productions<ref>{{cite web|url=http://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/moviedetails/63215?sid=2fd1c893-a718-4270-9705-01129dcaa922&sr=3.9971654&cp=1&pos=0|title=Seed of Chucky  (2004)|work=[[AFI Catalog of Feature Films]]|access-date=February 3, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" co