93/ranking/cd_album/ |title=\u30b9\u30d1\u30a4\u30b9\u30fb\u30ac\u30fc\u30eb\u30ba\u306e\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u58f2\u308a\u4e0a\u3052\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 |trans-title=Spice Girls album sales ranking |website=[[Oricon]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=6 August 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201222647/http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/95993/ranking/cd_album/ |archivedate=1 February 2014}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysian Albums ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FA8EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA55&dq=Spice+Girls |title=Hits of the World |magazine=Billboard |volume=109 |issue=7 |date=15 February 1997 |page=55 |issn=0006-2510 |accessdate=6 August 2017 |via=Google Books}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n{{album chart|New Zealand|1|artist=Spice Girls|album=Spice|rowheader=true|accessdate=28 March 2012}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Norway|1|artist=Spice Girls|album=Spice|rowheader=true|accessdate=28 March 2012}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Portuguese Albums ([[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Fonogr\u00e1fica Portuguesa|AFP]])<ref name=\"MM-1997-04-19\"/>\n| 1\n|-\n{{album chart|Scotland|1|date=19961110|rowheader=true|accessdate=24 February 2015}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Spanish Albums ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|AFYVE]])<ref name=\"BB-1997-01-18\"/>\n| 1\n|-\n{{album chart|Sweden|1|artist=Spice Girls|album=Spice|rowheader=true|accessdate=28 March 2012}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Switzerland|5|artist=Spice Girls|album=Spice|rowheader=true|accessdate=6 August 2017}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Taiwanese International Albums ([[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]])<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ifpi.org.tw/chart/1997/intl13.htm |title=IFPI Taiwan International Top 10 \u2013 Year: 1997, Week: 13 |website=[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]] Taiwan |accessdate=25 November 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19980224062521/http://ifpi.org.tw/chart/1997/intl13.